(1, 'One mile move', 'I am somewhere on earth. I walk one mile south, one west and one mile north and I end up back where I started. Where am I?', 'Noth Pole', 'There are more then one points on the Earth.', 2),
(5, 'Show me What you Got', 'Poor people have it. Rich people need it. If you eat it you die. What is it?', 'nothing', '', 0),
(6, 'Down we Go', 'What comes down but never goes up?', 'rain', '', 0),
(7, 'Feed me', 'If I drink, I die. If i eat, I am fine. What am I?', 'fire', '', 0),
(8, 'Got it?', 'If I have it, I donâ€™t share it. If I share it, I donâ€™t have it. What is it?', 'A Secret', '', 0),
(9, 'Weeping', 'What has a head but never weeps, has a bed but never sleeps, can run but never walks, and has a bank but no money?', 'A river', '', 0),
(10, 'Faith', 'What is something almost everyone as seen but no one will ever see again?', 'Yesterday', '', 0),
(11, 'Sleep tight', 'One night, a butcher, a baker and a candlestick maker go to a hotel. When they get their bill, however, itâ€™s for four people. Whoâ€™s the fourth person?', 'The knight', '', 0),
(12, 'Yum', 'What two things can you never eat for breakfast?', 'Lunch or dinner', '', 0),
(13, 'Holy ', 'What can you catch but not throw?', 'A cold', '', 0),
(14, 'Think', 'No sooner spoken than broken. What is it? ', 'Silence', '', 0),
(15, 'Cthulhu', 'This old one runs forever, but never moves at all. He has not lungs nor throat, but still a mighty roaring call. What is it?', 'A waterfall', '', 0),
(16, 'Mississipppi', 'A word I know, six letters it contains, remove one letter, and twelve remains. What am I?', 'Dozens', '', 0);
